parameters: Ahoy son, thank ye fer findin' me in the midst o'
these nasty natives!
I 'ave ne'er seen such injuries on livin' scallywags
afore. By all accounts these poor souls should 'ave
met thar maker a long time ago..
Truthfully I dunno what be keepin' them alive.
I'll keep goin', you should keep lookin' for the rest
o' the crew. You should meet up with us after!
Oh and take these! You may need them more than I.
You have gained 10 bombs!!
Press 'x' to unleash their
explosive potential.
Four down.. only one crewmember to go!
Then we can finally start looking for that ship to
scavenge parts from.
Thats number three, only two to go! It sure is a good
thing this jungle has a pretty linear structure.
Otherwise I might get totally lost!
Two ship hands down. I better keep looking, don't
want to be stuck here much longer.
Well I guess I'd better keep looking for the rest of
the crew.. only four more, how hard could it be?
Thats everyone!! I should probably go meet up
with everyone else in order to progress..
Ye go on ahead, I shall meet up wit' ye once I 'ave
a better idea o' what be goin on 'ere.
